{"tid":1584772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「大家誤解左」綠衫/黑衫唔一定係警察","createTime":"2019-09-21T10:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:07:54.000Z","uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c61f8dfe63464268606aa2e5fbaac6c5c287d9a","tid":1584772,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"我見大家都先入為主左，以為有一班著綠衫有武器嘅人係警察，或所謂畜龍係警察<br />\n<br />\n但我想問返，有無<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公開資料</strong></span>提過有套咁嘅制服？<br />\n我google極都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n如果真心要話佢地係警察，咁依套最多係便服！<br />\n<br />\n但著便衣執法係要show委任証（公開資料）（圖1 pt 2)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJt4K6J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJt4K6J.png&h=50c7e6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWndDrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWndDrJ.png&h=fb8d17dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家要分清楚係咩警察先<br />\n<br />\n如果見到自稱警察但無show委任証就要小心係冒警<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外求律師撚fact check，如果有熱心市民想行使公民拘捕權，應該係咩條件下先得</span></strong></em></ins>"},{"pid":"ab68e6476bd5a3daf59e0c81fb3cdabc22ddbe6a","tid":1584772,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f925c9bf126a797caa00e741d21059f9b997fb61","tid":1584772,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"deb213517653563dbd8bf9bc417a740ea910b650","tid":1584772,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"今日似乎中央按照咗劇本做嘢<br />\n<br />\n【香港危局】十一前北京真要動手？知情者爆廣東有異動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e1443ba733f14bb73e02725181c1409a58688e4e","tid":1584772,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"如果大家都唔知警察制服係點，同時又無委任証，自衛可以合法？<br />\n<br />\n好似岳義士根本無襲警，佢只係見到有緣衫攪香港市民，先搵命博去救人，因為當時緣衫係有武器嘅恐怖分子，完全唔知係警察"}]}